    - isBusinessKey
    - isLastModifiedColumn
    - isChangeTracking
    - isSystemCreateDate
    - isSystemUpdateDate
    - isSystemEndDate
    - isSystemCurrentFlag
    - isSystemVersion

Output:
- No direct data output
- Returns a FAIL-select statement if validation fails
- Otherwise allows query execution to proceed
===================================================================================================== #}
